{"tid":257220,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"獌迷車p 反獌勿入","createTime":"2017-05-25T05:57:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-25T10:22:21.000Z","uid":38543,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4971297bdc685619f8c4b9634d6b66cbc4360314","tid":257220,"uid":38543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T05:57:41.000Z","msg":"是咁的，呢個星期五，我唔去浦了。夜晚出車。 <br />\n我地book 了3 款車。第一隻 大巴 , 租的。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/25/135519_201b52602bd86751b393b7c9dcf1c0da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F25%2F135519_201b52602bd86751b393b7c9dcf1c0da.jpg&h=805d0dc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n坐100人的，長8呎幾。 <br />\n<br />\n另一隻, 私伙的紅van 坐16人 德國式 襯返我地曼聯紅<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/25/135600_32b37cc9625a8ba154d49f34b74ecfe4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F25%2F135600_32b37cc9625a8ba154d49f34b74ecfe4.jpg&h=0db11377&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我中意呢隻多d，大少少，寫意d。 <br />\n<br />\n重有一架jazz 都係用返我地曼聯紅<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/25/135642_c940e67e0ef9361333ffd3e0a481a650.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F25%2F135642_c940e67e0ef9361333ffd3e0a481a650.jpg&h=9cd70ce3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n搞手會買好多酒。 <br />\n<br />\n星期五 , 7點將軍澳碼頭集合 <br />\n<br />\n男仔：$500 位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女仔：Model , 靚女免費。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n普通女仔： 唔比黎 <br />\n<br />\n來吧靚女，識d俾得起$500去車p的人吧。 <br />\n<br />\np.s. 呢d車p無得賺，搞手只求打個和，大家開開心心玩返晚。"},{"pid":"e34f517091f7ada56a09872a9b8c5497a8b05aa6","tid":257220,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T05:59:18.000Z","msg":"車路士都取消左勝利巡遊"},{"pid":"e58e152863d47a3e1c1f6d734bcb3b1371a115c5","t